<br>
I still support the idea of the Epic Orb being a focus item for 61+ pets. However, asking for yet another increase in power for the pet at this point is simply too much. It was already increased recently, it is a brute.  <br>
<br>
You want the epic to be better because of PoP zones, yet imagine how would effect those level 51+ magicians with epics?  We already have level 52 epic mage + cleric duo wiping out much of Sebillis right now because the pet is so powerful.  You would triviailize most of the game outside of PoP by making the pet even more than it is now.<br>
<br>
So find another solution, for example-<br>
<br>
Epic focus item quest (PoP required).  This quest would yield an item which would be <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>required level 61</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to equip and act as a focus item for epic.  Of course the magicians with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>gloves of dark summoning</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> might complain if their uber-loot got replaced by a quest anybody could do.<br>
